This directory contains the dddfs that is a distributed file system. 

written by Miki Horiuchi <mikity@logos.ic.i.u-tokyo.ac.jp>
Created: 3 Mar. 2012
Last Modified: 22 May 2012

== INSTALL ==

== HOW TO USE ==
[metadata server]
 % dddfs --meta [meta_dir]
meta_dir: path of directory to manage metadata

[servers]
 % dddfs --server --meta_addr [meta_addr] [data_dir]
meta_addr: IP or hostname of metadata server
data_dir: path of directory to manage data

[clients]
 % dddfs --client --meta_addr [meta_addr] [mount_point]
meta_addr: IP or hostname of metadata server
mount_point: path of directory to mount dddfs to

== UNMOUNT ==